{"tid":1534830,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"10號銅鑼灣要人丫！！！","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T05:37:11.000Z","uid":163519,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dda17d7759cdde0a626b4fb9513f18c22e829859","tid":1534830,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:36:07.000Z","msg":"係丫！<span style=\"color: red;\">10號</span>香港大球場要人丫！！！香港人唔好同我講唔撐香港隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隊波仲要冇中國兩個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2022卡塔爾世界盃暨2023中國亞洲盃聯合外圍賽第二圈（C組）<br />\n2019年9月10日<br />\n晚上8時<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港</strong> 對 伊朗</span><br />\n<br />\n票價<br />\n成人：180元；<br />\n特惠：40元<br />\n（凡於9月9日或之前於門市或Cityline購票通購買單場門票，均可豁免Cityline購票通手續費。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://venue.cityline.com/utsvInternet/enrollment/action/event.do?actionFwd=eventDetail&amp;event=31912&amp;activityCode=EAFF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvenue.cityline.com%2FutsvInternet%2Fenrollment%2Faction%2Fevent.do%3FactionFwd%3DeventDetail%26event%3D31912%26activityCode%3DEAFF&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=e7df4f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://venue.cityline.com/utsvInternet/enrollment/action/event.do?actionFwd=eventDetail&amp;event=31912&amp;activityCode=EAFF</a> 快啲買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又話9月繼續抗爭唔好俾佢完，係咪香港大球場4萬個位都坐唔滿丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n場波又會播<span style=\"color: navy;\">義勇軍進行軍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又可以不停叫口號（港超啲手足叫足全場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）如果有波衫記得著埋去！！好多位球員都係手足嚟，新聞都報哂喇，你唔係唔撐番佢地嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"8bb744af0f14e500756178fdf9eb25e395c8f972","tid":1534830,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41d1d0b444bf99c491cc98fa15254dab00e4bbce","tid":1534830,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73cdaf0424b14393050c9d76a0e2042799b2e35a","tid":1534830,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"自推十連(1/10)"},{"pid":"748093193a86ddb7e5604c339c13d5bcf01782ba","tid":1534830,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連(2/10)"},{"pid":"7b85498c223fc1867aae3329f9f93e356e110229","tid":1534830,"uid":31906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:40:49.000Z","msg":"伊朗咪話唔黎香港踢"},{"pid":"457a276e968ffa4ac42e119bb019adf781dc0598","tid":1534830,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"而家伊朗未必嚟<br />\n唔駛推"},{"pid":"817cac6f19e9bb10294c837c60d31d3812af7b39